<subSubSection id="C370656FFF85FFB0FF5B4C1257C4FC1C" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8BD536E4FF85FFB0FF5B4C1257C4FC1C" blockId="9.[151,1436,746,1603]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
TYPE LOCALITY. Originally “in deserti australioris collibus ardentissimis” (
<bibRefCitation id="EFFB4B15FF85FFB0FBE04C0D52C5FCE4" author="Pallas, P. S." box="[1068,1213,815,840]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" refId="ref61618" refString="Pallas, P. S. (1771) Reise durch verschiedene Provinzen des Russisches Reichs. Kaiserlichen Akademie der Wissenschaften, St. Petersburg, 504 pp." type="book" year="1771">Pallas 1771</bibRefCitation>
); restricted to the “Inderskija Gory, Gebiet des unteren Uralflusses” [region of lower Ural River, W 
<collectingCountry id="F37D7674FF85FFB0FBAD4C70529FFCC7" box="[1121,1255,850,875]" name="Kazakhstan" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Kazakhstan</collectingCountry>
] by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFFB4B15FF85FFB0FAEC4C715743FC22" author="Mertens, R. &amp; Muller, L." pageId="9" pageNumber="10" pagination="1 - 62" refId="ref58855" refString="Mertens, R. &amp; Muller, L. (1928) Liste der Amphibien und Reptilien Europas. Abhandlungen der Senckenbergischen Naturfoschenden Gesellschaft, 41, 1 - 62." type="journal article" year="1928">Mertens &amp; Müller (1928)</bibRefCitation>
. This restriction was not accompanied by a 
<typeStatus id="54D18846FF85FFB0FCF04C5755DBFC22" box="[828,931,885,910]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">lectotype</typeStatus>
or 
<typeStatus id="54D18846FF85FFB0FC014C54525EFC22" box="[973,1062,886,910]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">neotype</typeStatus>
designation and is therefore not valid as such (
<bibRefCitation id="EFFB4B15FF85FFB0FEFA4CB557C9FC1C" author="Uetz, P." box="[310,433,919,944]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" refId="ref67280" refString="Uetz, P. (2013) The Reptile database. Available from: http: // www. reptile-database. org / (accessed 8 July 2014)" type="url" year="2013">Uetz 2013</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
